<li><a data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="5184026b-3c7c-4537-9d22-8afb6aad845d" href="/sites/lagrandesd.org/files/inline-files/COVID-19-cases-in-Oregon-schools.pdf" rel="nofollow">Oregon Health Authority â COVID-19 Cases in Oregon Schools</a></li>
